title: 011 - The Pod Reacts To Covid-19
description: On today's show, the guys react to all the craziness stemming from Covid19 (Coronavirus) shutting down virtually everything and putting us into a situation we haven't been in before, plus give their best options for check it aht/don't check it aht while in a quarantine. Stay safe everybody. Enjoy.
